5:
Oh man, street food is so great. So
much different stuff you don't
normally get a chance to eat!
8:
Yeah, but every once in a while you

12:
Huh? No way! I told you I don't have

15:
Isn't that the guy who was running a

23:

26:

29:

32:
Allow me to step in and help the

41:
Yes. As you know, our legendary

42:

47:
Seems like a pretty clear-cut case

56:

58:
Have you not heard of INVESTMENT?
It's simple really, you supply funds to

Up-and-coming businesses need a

all!
61:
Those guys didn't look like they were
here to help.
65:
A debt you can't collect on is a big

COUNTING on him not being able to

69:

74:
Exactly! And the reason for that is
that word got out I was the one
financing the shop! I'm being
targeted, you see, hah-hah!
79:
That sounds very much like a YOU
problem.
83:
Ah, but Alk, mon ami... Perhaps you
could nonetheless lend your pal
Regis a hand in this matter?
85:
With your incredible cooking skills, I
know you can make a master chef
out of my man here! Get him to
cook delectableâ€”and
PROFITABLEâ€”dishes!
89:
Um... I... *sigh*
Listen, just 'cause I can cook a few

93:
Is that so? Hmm, and here I thought

96:
Listen, Mr. Alk... I'd be super grateful if
you would just try! It won't do any
harm, right?
102:
Okay... But, I don't think I can do this
alone. I'm going to need to call for

107:
But of course I'll assist you. I wouldn't
pass up on an opportunity to
instruct someone in the wonderful

110:
You mean my teacher is gonna be a

113:
Excuse me! That's no way to refer to

117:
Well I'll be. A yokai chef. Your
connections in other worlds never
cease to amaze me.
122: So. We off to the next place, or?
125:
My, you have a good sense for these
things. I take it you're coming along?
128:
Heh, I knew there was no way that's
all you had up your sleeve. Besides,

132:
G-god damn you! The hell are you

135:
Mr. Register... I would have thought

138:
You'll have to excuse that little

140:
Besides, I've come to talk business.
Though I hope you'll forgive me

142:
Fairly? You mean like paying

That kind of "fair"?
144:
I was more referring to going

147:
Listen here, Mr. Register. We have a

157:
"We have a very specific way of

162:
And this, my technologically

165:
Bye daddy! Have a good day at

167:
When are you going to finally
divorce your wife, huh?
169: What the hell is the meaning of this?!
172:
When it comes to underhanded

174:
I have a new proposal for youâ€”one

178:
Which one of you was the bad guy

183:
Hahaha. I trust you'll be kind enough

189:
Welcome back. Done with your

193:
Sh-shady? Was it that obvious?
Wait a moment. All these

196:
What sort of magic did you use to

203:
I asked Shirano for a recipe so easy

So, here you go. Miso soupâ€”with

213:

219:
I don't think I've ever heard miso
soup described that way, but sure.
